# DEPRECATED — Caddy routing is managed centrally by the service registry.
#
# All HR subdomains (www, api, blog, docs, admin, odoo) are configured in:
#   ~/src/registry/caddy/Caddyfile  (Group 6: HR Platform)
#
# Port mapping (host → container, used by the registry proxy):
#   www.hr.svc.assistance.bg   → 5020 (hr-www, Next.js)
#   api.hr.svc.assistance.bg   → 5080 (hr-api, Go)
#   blog.hr.svc.assistance.bg  → 5023 (hr-blog, Astro)
#   docs.hr.svc.assistance.bg  → 5021 (hr-docs, Astro Starlight)
#   admin.hr.svc.assistance.bg → 5014 (hr-admin, Vite SPA)
#   odoo.hr.svc.assistance.bg  → 8069/8072 (Odoo ERP)
#
# Do NOT add a caddy service to podman-compose — the registry proxy handles TLS and routing.
